Hello Foodies, Welcome to Wish My Food. The most awaited recipe is Hyderabadi Chicken Dum Biryani. Let's see how to prepare this. If you follow this as it is, you will get the perfect restaurant style biryani taste every time. This is a very tasty biryani. Let's start.

